                                <para>*These values are for Class 9.8 bolts; all other values are for Class 10.9
                                    bolts.
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                    </tbody>
                </tgroup>
            </table>
            <specpara>
                <note>
                    <para>These torque values are to be used only where no other specific torque is given in a service
                        manual or other publication.
                    </para>
                </note>
            </specpara>
